Class AuditEntity

java.lang.Object
com.github.ilim.backend.entity.AuditEntity
Direct Known Subclasses:
Course, CourseModule, CourseModuleItem, CoursePurchase, InstructorApp, Question, QuestionOption, Quiz, QuizAttempt, User, UserAnswer, UserAnswerOption, Video
@MappedSuperclass public class AuditEntity extends Object
Base class for entities that require audit information.

Provides fields for tracking creation and update timestamps. Automatically sets these fields using the AuditListener.
